# RHEL 10: https://issues.redhat.com/browse/RHEL-94536
/hardening/.+/rpm_verify_(ownership|permissions)
    rhel <= 9.6 or rhel == 10.0

# https://issues.redhat.com/browse/RHEL-92260
/hardening/.+/ism_o/rpm_verify_permissions
    rhel == 9

